Class CharacterMarkerSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.symbology.fmap.mapcontext.rendering.symbol.impl.AbstractCartographicSupport

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, CartographicSupport, IPrintable, ISymbol, ISymbol_v2, IMarkerSymbol, IMarkerSymbol_v2, Persistent

    public class CharacterMarkerSymbol
extends AbstractMarkerSymbol
implements IMarkerSymbol_v2
    Allows to use a source of TrueType characters to define the marker that will substitute the symbol.If the picture is defined in a source, the performance is more agile.
